      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty! It's in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the assembly line. I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! I'm happy to answer any questions, so don't be shy\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
