    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood lies the legendary S54B32 power unit, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a pristine chassis free of any fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, delivering the telepathic steering response these cars are renowned for. A true turnkey collector piece for the discerning driver.",
