      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m listing this absolute gem that is in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage, kept smoke-free, and the paint is so shiny you can practically see your reflection in it. It drives like a total dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
